headline: NetApp (NasdaqGS:NTAP) Appoints Frank Pelzer Joining Diverse Board Amid Flat Share Price
summary: NetApp (NasdaqGS:NTAP) recently appointed Frank Pelzer to its Board of Directors, reflecting a commitment to leadership renewal with 40% of board members appointed in the past five years. During the same period, NetApp's stock performance remained essentially flat over the week, aligning with broader market trends as the S&P 500 and Nasdaq Composite also experienced modest declines amid investor concerns over new tariffs and economic data. Despite Pelzer's extensive tech-sector experience...
